<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Data Processing Agreement</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #1f2937;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 48px 40px;
            background: white;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 36px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .doc-title {
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #111827;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.03em;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .doc-subtitle {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .doc-subtitle strong {
            color: #111827;
        }

        .security-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 14px;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            background: #eff6ff;
            color: #2563eb;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .parties-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 24px;
            margin: 28px 0;
        }

        .party-card {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .party-label {
            font-size: 11px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .party-name {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .party-details {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .content {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #374151;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .clause {
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .clause h4 {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .clause p {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .clause ul,
        .clause ol {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        .clause li {
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .data-details {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 16px 0;
        }

        .data-details th {
            background: #f9fafb;
            text-align: left;
            padding: 10px 14px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #6b7280;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            width: 35%;
        }

        .data-details td {
            padding: 10px 14px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #111827;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
        }

        .security-box {
            background: #eff6ff;
            border: 1px solid #bfdbfe;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .security-box h4 {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1e40af;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .security-box ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        .security-box li {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #1e3a5f;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .breach-box {
            background: #fef2f2;
            border: 1px solid #fecaca;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .breach-box h4 {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #991b1b;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .breach-box p {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #7f1d1d;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .signature-section {
            margin-top: 40px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 32px;
        }

        .sig-card {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 24px;
        }

        .sig-title {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .sig-field {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .sig-field-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .sig-field-line {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #d1d5db;
            height: 24px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 48px;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 24px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #9ca3af;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="doc-title">Data Processing Agreement</div>
        <div class="doc-subtitle"><strong>Effective Date:</strong> {{effectiveDate}} &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Agreement
                No:</strong> {{#if agreementNumber}}{{agreementNumber}}{{else}}DPA-2024-001{{/if}}</div>
        <div class="security-badge">DPDP Act 2023 Compliant</div>
    </div>

    <div class="parties-grid">
        <div class="party-card">
            <div class="party-label">Data Controller</div>
            <div class="party-name">{{controllerName}}</div>
            <div class="party-details">{{{controllerAddress}}}{{#if controllerEmail}}<br>{{controllerEmail}}{{/if}}
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="party-card">
            <div class="party-label">Data Processor</div>
            <div class="party-name">{{processorName}}</div>
            <div class="party-details">{{{processorAddress}}}{{#if processorEmail}}<br>{{processorEmail}}{{/if}}</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>This Data Processing Agreement ("DPA") is entered into as part of the service agreement between the parties.
            This DPA sets out the terms for the processing of personal data by the Data Processor on behalf of the Data
            Controller in compliance with the Digital Personal Data Protection Act, 2023 and other applicable data
            protection laws.</p>

        <div class="clause">
            <h4>1. Definitions</h4>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>"Personal Data"</strong> means any data about an individual who is identifiable by or in
                    relation to such data.</li>
                <li><strong>"Processing"</strong> means any operation performed on personal data including collection,
                    storage, use, disclosure, and deletion.</li>
                <li><strong>"Data Principal"</strong> means the individual to whom the personal data relates.</li>
                <li><strong>"Data Breach"</strong> means unauthorized access, disclosure, or loss of personal data.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <h4>2. Subject Matter & Details of Processing</h4>
            <table class="data-details">
                <tr>
                    <th>Purpose of Processing</th>
                    <td>{{{processingPurpose}}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>Nature of Processing</th>
                    <td>{{#if processingNature}}{{processingNature}}{{else}}Collection, storage, analysis, and
                        reporting{{/if}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>Categories of Data</th>
                    <td>{{#if dataCategories}}{{dataCategories}}{{else}}Personal identifiers, contact information, usage
                        data{{/if}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>Data Subjects</th>
                    <td>{{#if dataSubjects}}{{dataSubjects}}{{else}}Employees, customers, business contacts{{/if}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>Duration</th>
                    <td>{{#if duration}}{{duration}}{{else}}Duration of the service agreement{{/if}}</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <h4>3. Obligations of Data Processor</h4>
            <ol>
                <li>Process personal data only on documented instructions from the Data Controller.</li>
                <li>Ensure that persons authorized to process the data have committed themselves to confidentiality.
                </li>
                <li>Implement appropriate technical and organizational security measures.</li>
                <li>Not engage another processor without prior written authorization from the Data Controller.</li>
                <li>Assist the Data Controller in fulfilling obligations related to Data Principal requests.</li>
                <li>Delete or return all personal data upon termination of services, unless retention is required by
                    law.</li>
                <li>Make available all information necessary to demonstrate compliance and allow for audits.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <div class="security-box">
            <h4>4. Security Measures</h4>
            <p>The Data Processor shall implement the following minimum security measures:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Encryption of personal data both in transit (TLS 1.2+) and at rest (AES-256)</li>
                <li>Regular backup and disaster recovery procedures</li>
                <li>Access control with role-based permissions and multi-factor authentication</li>
                <li>Regular security assessments, penetration testing, and vulnerability scanning</li>
                <li>Incident detection, response, and logging mechanisms</li>
                <li>Physical security of data processing facilities</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="breach-box">
            <h4>5. Data Breach Notification</h4>
            <p>The Data Processor shall notify the Data Controller of any personal data breach without undue delay and
                in any event within <strong>{{#if breachNotificationPeriod}}{{breachNotificationPeriod}}{{else}}72
                    hours{{/if}}</strong> of becoming aware of the breach. The notification shall include the nature of
                the breach, categories and approximate number of data subjects affected, likely consequences, and
                measures taken to address the breach.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <h4>6. Sub-Processing</h4>
            <p>The Data Processor shall not engage any sub-processor without prior written authorization from the Data
                Controller. Where sub-processing is authorized, the Data Processor shall impose the same data protection
                obligations as set out in this DPA on the sub-processor.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <h4>7. Data Transfers</h4>
            <p>The Data Processor shall not transfer personal data outside India without the prior written consent of
                the Data Controller and unless adequate safeguards are in place as required under applicable law,
                including the Digital Personal Data Protection Act, 2023.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <h4>8. Audits & Inspections</h4>
            <p>The Data Processor shall allow the Data Controller or an authorized third-party auditor to conduct
                inspections and audits to verify compliance with this DPA, subject to reasonable notice and during
                normal business hours.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <h4>9. Term & Termination</h4>
            <p>This DPA shall remain in effect for the duration of the service agreement. Upon termination, the Data
                Processor shall, at the Data Controller's choice, return or securely delete all personal data within
                <strong>{{#if deletionPeriod}}{{deletionPeriod}}{{else}}30 days{{/if}}</strong>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <h4>10. Governing Law</h4>
            <p>This DPA shall be governed by the laws of India, including the Digital Personal Data Protection Act, 2023
                and the Information Technology Act, 2000. Any disputes shall be subject to the jurisdiction of courts in
                {{#if jurisdiction}}{{jurisdiction}}{{else}}Bangalore, India{{/if}}.</p>
        </div>

        <p><strong>IN WITNESS WHEREOF,</strong> the parties have executed this Data Processing Agreement as of the date
            first written above.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="signature-section">
        <div class="sig-card">
            <div class="sig-title">Data Controller</div>
            <div class="sig-field">
                <div class="sig-field-label">Authorized Signature</div>
                <div class="sig-field-line"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="sig-field">
                <div class="sig-field-label">Name: {{controllerName}}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="sig-field">
                <div class="sig-field-label">Date</div>
                <div class="sig-field-line"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sig-card">
            <div class="sig-title">Data Processor</div>
            <div class="sig-field">
                <div class="sig-field-label">Authorized Signature</div>
                <div class="sig-field-line"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="sig-field">
                <div class="sig-field-label">Name: {{processorName}}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="sig-field">
                <div class="sig-field-label">Date</div>
                <div class="sig-field-line"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>Data Processing Agreement — Compliant with DPDP Act, 2023</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>